title: Knock It Off
description: When the Professor's college roommate sees his old pal's brilliant creations, he decides to cash in on the popularity of the Powerpuffs.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Bored to Be Wild
description: Mega Man teams up with his crush, Ashley Adderley, to solve a series of science riddles left by Chemical Man, who's plotting to turn all the city's metal into rubber.

title: Jugo arcoiris
description: Después de desafiarse unos a otros a tomar el Latte de Pegaso de Chef, Izzy y Jude están llenos de energía y Duncan y Courtney hacen un viaje por carretera para tratar de reemplazar la bebida antes de que Chef descubra que desapareció.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Cool Uncles
description: The Titans take a trip to Wackadoodles, but Trigon makes Raven babysit her little brothers.

title: #BreakingNews
description: Lois Lane's attempt to get an internship at the Daily Planet leads to her trying to unmask the Super Hero Girls, which forces the girls to a battle of wits with their greatest nemesis yet.

title: Principito perricornio
description: Puppycorn por fin se da cuenta de que es un príncipe, iy quiere estar a cargo del reino por una vez! A pesar de las preocupaciones de sus amigos, Unikitty permite que Puppycorn sea el rey, pero pronto, el poder absoluto en las manos del cachorro se le hace difícil de manejar, y sus ideas no son lo que se diría muy geniales. ¿Podrán removerlo del poder mientras evitan un levantamiento del pueblo?

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Cluckwork Orange
description: After befriending a chicken with a bad attitude at a petting zoo, Jude is followed back to school by the chicken. He defends the bad bird's behavior until he can defend it no longer.

title: Lightfall Part 2
description: Lord Obsidian attacks the Lighthouse, but Mega Man overcomes his insecurity and works with his family to repel the big bad, who's rescued at the last second by a mysterious lieutenant, Namagem.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 1
description: As the Autobots on the Ark prepare to land on Cybertron, Chromia and Perceptor attempt to escape Decepticon captivity.

title: Cambiando Objetos
description: Axel y el equipo luchan contra la Princesa SugarSalt por la posesión del martillo de Bearbarian, que le vendió uno de los suyos: iGalileo!

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Who's the Fake?!/Trouble Busters! 2
description: With the reveal that Haavik is a shapeshifting Alien, the ABs start to get super-paranoid, realizing that ANYONE could be Haavik in disguise. The suspicion quickly turns inward, and the ABs are left wondering if they have an imposter among them!/ A kid brawler named Oliver has lost his Bakugan! This seems like a job for the Trouble Busters. The Awesome Brawlers help him chase down and try to catch the elusive Bakugan, who leads them on a wild goose chase through Los Volmos.

title: Queen of the Munce
description: Jay, Nya and Lloyd are led deep into the Mines of Shintaro by Murt, who brings them back to the Munce "Home- Cave" - a settlement deep in the mountain. There, complications arise when they meet the Munce Queen, Murtessa, who takes a liking to Jay.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Forced Kin
description: A terrible, evil menace from outer space descends upon Townville. The girls must fight evil with evil so they seek the advice of Mojo Jojo.

title: Tragic Magic
description: After Richard puts on an amateur magic show, Dr. Fox becomes obsessed with figuring out how his science-defying tricks are done. But as she sets about using all of her genius intellect finding experimental ways to pull off the little pup's party tricks, will she accidentally ruin the wonder of magic?

title: Pintura dolorosa
description: Leshawna inventa una pelea con globos llenos de pintura para ver quién va al parque de diversiones con ella.

title: The Skull Sorcerer
description: Separated from the others, Cole must trust his instincts and make the right choices to find his way to the surface to alert King Vangelis of the dangerous Skull Sorcerer.

title: La Super Increible Aventura en Balsa
description: Unikitty y Hawkodile están "perdidos en el mar," varados en una balsa juntos. Hawkodile ve esto como una oportunidad para mostrarle a Unikitty que está preparado para cualquier cosa con sus habilidades de experto en supervivencia, pero para su sorpresa, todos sus planes fracasan, mientras que la tonta postura de Unikitty de "todo saldrá bien, vamos a divertirnos" está funcionando de una manera genial. ¿Será Hawkodile capaz de soltar su exceso de preparación para salvarlos a ambos, o acaso la diversión caprichosa de Unikitty será su perdición?

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Ventila-hala
description: Chef le confisca la mega-bola a Owen y la guarda en su oficina. Duncan, viendo una oportunidad para conseguir ayuda escapando de la guardaería, lidera un equipo de fuga por los conductos del aire acondicionado para recuperarla.

title: Everett's Trap/Kazami vs. Mc Q
description: Shun and Masato head to Tokyo's Battle Island to discuss plans for hosting public Bakugan battles. Upon landing, they quickly learn it's a set up! The two are now stranded and faced with heaps of brawlers, who are all looking to bring them down!/ Shun and Masato manage to fend off a horde of brawlers on Battle Island, but they quickly learn that was only a diversion- one of Kazami's research centers is under siege. The two must find a way off the island and head off to defend the research center.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: (Not) Your Father's Mouse-Stache
description: It's the battle of the moustaches when Tom accidentally drinks a hair tonic potion left behind by Jerry and Butch realizes he needs to acquire some facial hair of his own if he is to compete for Toodles and Dollface's attentions.

title: Lightfall Part 1
description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

title: Counting Sheep
description: Tom and Jerry are hired by Dixie Wolf to find all the sheep that have gone missing.

title: Bakugan Battle Circus/Ebony Manor
description: Shun and Dan head to the Bakugan circus for a little fun, but the fun is interrupted when the star Bakugan are too exhausted to perform. Shun and Dan know the show must go on, and step in to lend a hand. Things go as planned until the evil Ringleader attempts to bring down the big top performance./ Lightning reunites with an old frenemy - Ebony. This time the kitty queen of the streets has a new home and is living a life of luxury with her new master.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Magia Tragica
description: Cuando Richard monta un espectáculo de magia amateur, la Dra. Fox se obsesiona por descubrir cómo se hacen esos trucos que desafían la ciencia. Pero mientras se propone usar todo su intelecto para encontrar formas experimentales de hacer los trucos que vio en la fiesta del cachorro, ¿acaso arruinará accidentalmente el asombro de la magia?

title: Balloonatics
description: Tom and Jerry fight each other with the balloons that Rick has placed all over the house to surprise Ginger on their anniversary.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: All Chalked Up
description: Him tricks Bubbles into bringing her chalk drawings to life, who then proceed to wreak havoc in Townsville.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Safari Joe
description: While minding her own business, Cheetara is caught in a trap set by Safari Joe, the famously annoying hunter! After escaping, she rallies the other ThunderCats to help her stop Joe once and for all, by turning the tables and capturing him!

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Little Prince Puppycorn
description: Puppycorn finally realizes he's a prince, so he wants to be in charge of the kingdom for once! Despite their friends' concerns, Unikitty makes Puppycorn ruler but realizes absolute power in the hands of the pup is too much for him to handle and his ideas aren't exactly great. Can they remove him from power while keeping the kingdom from revolting?

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Helter Shelter/Power Lunch
description: Helter Shelter: Bubbles has a habit of saving helpless animals and the Professor is sick of it. When Bubbles brings a baby whale home, she and her sisters have a whale of a time hiding this new addition./Power Lunch: The Gangreen Gang shoplifts from a mini-mart, shoveling loads of food down their throats as fast as possible. When the girls fire at them with their laser vision, a strange reaction occurs.

title: Venthalla
description: Owen has his super ball confiscated and locked up in Chef's office. Duncan, seeing an opportunity to get help escaping the daycare, leads an away team into the vents to recover Owen's ball.

title: El pollo maniaco
description: Después de hacerse amigo de un pollo con mala actitud en un zoológico de contacto, este lo sigue de regreso a la escuela. Él defiende la mala conducta del ave hasta que ya no puede seguir haciéndolo.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ninos vergonzosos
description: Owen teme perder a su mejor amigo Noah que se va a una escuela militar.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 2
description: The Autobots distract the Decepticons with an all-out assault on the Threshold of the Well while Bee, Hot Rod, and Cheetor split off for the real mission…

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: The Real Fall!
description: An entire episode chronicles the ninja's most bizarre adventure yet: in which Cole, Princess Vania and Master Wu fall down a seemingly endless tunnel, into the bowels of Shintaro Mountain.

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: De Puntitas
description: Después de un avistamiento de Porcupunk, Axel lidera una misión de reconocimiento que lenta pero seguramente demuestra ser una caza de gansos salvaje ideada por Sarge, quien en secreto persigue un pasatiempo que teme compartir con sus compañeros de equipo.

title: Senor Casero
description: El propietario amenazó a Master Frown y a Brock con desalojarlos a menos que arreglen el daño que le hicieron a su apartamento. Preocupado, Brock invita a Unikitty y a la pandilla para que los ayuden. En lugar de hacer lo que los chicos quieren en su casa, Unikitty procede a hacer lo que ella quiere. Al darse cuenta de su error, devuelve el apartamento a su antiguo estado asqueroso, pero ahora Frown y Brock están en peligro de desalojo de nuevo. Deben aliarse a Unikitty y la banda para luchar contra el malvado casero y salvar su hogar.

title: Grup Jam
description: Grup invents the "new" sport of basketball, but the stakes are too high for the Warriors to let him play the Galacton team, as the winner shall rule the Kingdom of Rhyboflaven.

title: Chutes and Tatters
description: Tom's assigned laundry duty at the estate and Jerry's determined to soil the job.

title: No sin mis choco-lletas
description: Noah intenta rescatar los chocolates que Owen olvidó afuera.

title: Butter Wall
description: When Beast Boy declares the Earth is a pancake, the Titans set sail to find out.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 1
description: Megatron's jubilation at destroying the Ark is short-lived as he realizes the ship was a decoy — the Autobots have landed on Cybertron.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: #CrashCourse
description: When a high-speed chase breaks out during her driver's test, Diana Prince's desire to fight evil clashes with her desire to undergo a World of Man teenage rite of passage, getting her license.

title: Bad Seed
description: Chef introduces the kids to agriculture by teaching them how to grow plants from seeds. But when Izzy shows her seed too much love, it turns into a monster that terrorizes the class.

title: On Your Toes
description: After a Porcupunk sighting, Axel leads a recon mission that slowly but surely proves to be a wild goose chase devised by Sarge, who's secretly pursuing a hobby that he's afraid to share with his teammates.

title: Guerra de Amigos
description: La princesa SugarSalt engaña a Axel para que salga con Cleo LeBall y usurpa su papel como líder del equipo, obligando a Zoe a intervenir y mantener los juguetes juntos.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 2
description: Chromia and Perceptor race to warn the Autobots that the Decepticons are waiting for them on Cybertron.

title: Champions of Breakfast
description: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

title: Summer Fun Day!
description: The Thundercats are exhausted from fighting bad guys all the time so Lion-O suggests they spend a relaxing summer fun day at the beach, with no fighting! Unfortunately the beach is home to the Crabmen, giant, clawed humanoids that fight anyone who steps on their sand! Looks like summer fun day might involve some fighting!

title: The Tome of Morrow
description: Noville's Magisword training with Vambre pays off and the Warriors invite him on a mission to an ancient cave in the Barren Faceland to find the rare and sacred book, the Tome of Morrow.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Dungeon Party
description: Having survived their fall into the mountain, Cole, Wu and Princess Vania befriend a motley group of survivors, called the Lowly, and are told the story of how they too ended up at "Rock-Bottom."

title: Super Amazing Raft Adventure
description: Unikitty and Hawkodile are "lost at sea", stranded on a raft together. Hawkodile sees this as an opportunity to show Unikitty that he's prepared for anything with his expertly-honed survival skills, but to his shock, all of his plans keep falling apart, while Unikitty's silly "it'll all work out, let's have fun" approach is somehow working great! Will Hawkodile manage to let go of his overpreparedness to save them both, or will Unikitty whimsical fun be their doom?

title: The Awesome Burger Brawl/Master and Apprentice
description: The Burger Joint is hosting a hamburger eating contest to promote their new Bakugan themed burger! The contest gets underway without a hitch, that is until Sophie and the Bakugan Preservation Society crash the event with a bakugan brawl!/ A wealthy man, Mr. Gold, has duped Storm and Ajit, and trapped them in his personal prison. But no prison can hold the cunning phantom thief Storm and his former apprentice, Ajit for long.

title: Landlord Lord
description: The Land Lord has threatened Master Frown and Brock with eviction unless they fix the damage they've done to their apartment. Worried, Brock invites Unikitty and the gang to help. Instead of doing what the guys want to their place, she proceeds to do what she wants. Realizing her error, she returns the apartment to its former disgusting state, but now Frown and Brock are in danger of eviction again. They must team up with Unikitty and the gang to battle the Land Lord and save their home.

title: The Old Gray Hair
description: After discovering a gray hair, Spikes decides he's too old to be the alpha of the house which sends Tom into full bully mode. Jerry will have to act fast to convince Spike he's still the alpha dog.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Acceso Denegado
description: Cuando Axel y el equipo intentan descubrir cuál es el arma secreta de Sarge Charge, son expulsados ​​de la casa por su sistema de seguridad recientemente actualizado y deben abrirse camino antes de que Madcap lo haga.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 1
description: While the battle rages on the surface, deep below ground Hot Rod faces off against an unexpected traitor, giving Cheetor and Bee time to get the Allspark to the Well.

title: License to Punch
description: Hawkodile's caught by the Action Police for bodyguarding without an Action License. He's can't protect the kingdom or do anything rad until he does, but the test at the DMV (The Department of Mayhem and Violence) is for nerds! Forced to retire his gloves, Hawkodile struggles to live a life without punching, so Unikitty vows to help her friend contain his urge to be action-y and study for the test. But there's more to the test than meets the eye.

title: Enter the Wood Man
description: Mega Man accidentally awakens Wood Man, who thinks it's still the Hard Age, sets off on a path of destruction toward Silicon City.

title: Lion-S
description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

title: Speed Demon
description: Batman has to enlist the help of Jason Blood, aka the Demon, when Brother Blood turns the Batmobile into a sentient, demonic entity.

title: Licencia para Golpear
description: A Hawkodile lo atrapa la policía de acción por trabajar como guardaespaldas sin licencia de acción. No puede proteger el reino ni hacer nada radical hasta tener la licencia, ipero la prueba en el Departamento de Caos y Violencia es para los nerds! Obligado a quitarse los guantes, Hawkodile lucha por vivir una vida sin golpes, por lo que Unikitty promete ayudar a su amigo a contener su impulso de entrar en acción y a estudiar para la prueba. Pero la prueba consiste en algo más de lo que parece.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Friend Wars
description: Princess SugarSalt dupes Axel into hanging out with Cleo LeBall and usurps his role as team leader, forcing Zoe to step in and keep the toys together.

title: Power Cycle
description: After replicating Elec Man's powers, an underslept/overcharged Mega Man goes on a 24/7 hero spree that ends up turning him into his own worst enemy.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: Duck Duck Juice
description: After daring each other to drink Chef's Pegasus Rainbow Latte, Izzy and Jude are jacked up like crazy and Duncan and Courtney take a road trip to try and replace the drink before Chef finds out it's gone.

title: A Fish Called Leshawna
description: After eating some mystery fish sticks, Leshawna achieves every little girl's dream and transforms into a mermaid!

title: Trial By Mino
description: Separated from the others, Kai and Zane discover a party of Geckles who suspect them of being in league with the Skull Sorcerer, and bring them before their leader, Chancellor Gulch, who subjects them to a "Trial-By-Mino."

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Prince Starling's Quest
description: Lion-O is happily playing with Snarf in their "Frolicking Field" and doesn't have a care in the world, unfortunately he's accidentally stomping all over the miniature village of the Micrits! The tiny people want to defeat the "giant orange monster" but such a quest would require a brave hero. Luckily, the Micrits have such a hero: Prince Starling! Now, let us the tell you the epic tale of Prince Starling as he journeys to find the fountain of growth and defeat the wicked Lion-O, who has no idea any of this is going on!

title: Bakugan Uproar/The Fusion Bakugan Sabrus
description: While the Awesome Brawlers' Bakugan squabble about what to watch on TV at Studio D, Haavik unleashes his newly created five-faction fusion Bakugan: Sabrus on the city of Los Volmos./ The Awesome Brawlers are in pursuit of Haavik and his new Bakugan, Sabrus but all they can find is the trail of destruction that Sabrus has left behind. They need to figure out where Haavik and his Bakugan will strike next and put an end to his rampage.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 2
description: Windblade, Wheeljack, and Teletraan-X make a play for Vector Sigma.

title: Gut Feelings
description: With help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword, the Warriors help get to the root of who stole all the vegetable Magiswords that belong to the angry bunny, Hoppus.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Ratar-O
description: The ThunderCats have gotten so good at defeating the Mutants of Plun-Darr that it's basically become routine. That all changes with the arrival of the Mutants' old leader: Ratar-O, wielder of the Sword of Plun-Darr! Uh-oh!

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: El oni y el dragon
